Identify the location of php.ini file used by running ./php -r "echo phpinfo();"
make changes to the php.ini file to allow creating phar by uncommenting and setting "phar.readonly = Off" 
make sure that Phar setting are updated by checking the output of ./php -r "echo phpinfo();"


copy the driver files buggy.php, correct.php, createphar.php, getcontents.php, getpharsignature.php, index.php 
and run-tests.sh script inside src/sapi/cli directory

execute the tests by running the run-tests.sh script using cmd: bash run-tests.sh
